            <head type="incipit">
               <supplied reason="XTF-compatibility">6 Cecil Place, ¶ near Town Hall, ¶ Prahran, ¶  17/2/83. ¶ Respected Sir, ¶  ¶ I shall feel greatly obliged if you will kindly inform me whether you are aware if the Kidney Bean (of which I enclose a p...</supplied>
            </head>
            <p rend="number" xml:lang="en">83.02.17a</p>
            <p rend="correspondent" xml:lang="en">From James Smith</p>
            <p rend="location" xml:lang="en">RB MSS M1, Library, Royal Botanic Gardens Melbourne.</p>
            <space dim="vertical" unit="lines" quantity="1"/>
            <p rend="letter"
               style="font-family: Geneva; font-size: 12pt; text-align: end; "
               xml:lang="en">
               <note xml:id="ftn1" type="footnote" n="1">
                  <p rend="Footnote"
                     style="font-family: Geneva; margin-left: 0.3335in; margin-right: 0in; text-indent: -0.3335in; font-size: 9pt; "
                     xml:lang="en">MS found with a specimen of <seg style="font-style: italic; ">Vigna luteola </seg>(MEL 1577012). The correspondent is James Smith (1815-1899).</p>
                  <p rend="Footnote"
                     style="font-family: Geneva; margin-left: 0.3335in; margin-right: 0in; text-indent: -0.3335in; font-size: 9pt; "
                     xml:lang="en">
                     <space dim="horizontal" extent="tab"/>MS is accompanied by a photograph, now very yellowed, dated and initialled: 'Feb 15. 1883. J. S.': 83-02-17a_image01.jpg</p>
                  <p rend="Footnote"
                     style="font-family: Geneva; margin-left: 0.3335in; margin-right: 0in; text-indent: -0.3335in; font-size: 9pt; "
                     xml:lang="en">
                     <space dim="horizontal" extent="tab"/>and a small watercolour of part of the plant showing flowers and pods on the stem: 83-02-17a_image02.jpg</p>
               </note>6 Cecil Place,</p>
            <p rend="letter"
               style="font-family: Geneva; font-size: 12pt; text-align: end; "
               xml:lang="en">near Town Hall,</p>
            <p rend="letter"
               style="font-family: Geneva; font-size: 12pt; text-align: end; "
               xml:lang="en">Prahran,<note xml:id="ftn2" type="footnote" n="2">
                  <p rend="Footnote"
                     style="font-family: Geneva; margin-left: 0.3335in; margin-right: 0in; text-indent: -0.3335in; font-size: 9pt; "
                     xml:lang="en">
                     <space unit="chars" quantity="1"/>
                     <space dim="horizontal" extent="tab"/>Melbourne.</p>
               </note> 17/2/83.</p>
            <p rend="letter"
               style="font-family: Geneva; font-size: 12pt; "
               xml:lang="en">Respected Sir,</p>
            <p rend="letter"
               style="font-family: Geneva; font-size: 12pt; "
               xml:lang="en">
               <space dim="horizontal" extent="tab"/>I shall feel greatly obliged if you will kindly inform me whether you are aware if the Kidney Bean (of which I enclose a photograph, &amp;c.) has been introduced and grown in this colony. Some seeds (small, nearly round, white, with black blotch at germ) were given to me as a curiosity two or three years since, and I have grown them the last two seasons, and believe they will furnish a very valuable addition to our cuisine — being remarkably prolific, not at all stringy, when cooked, and of fine flavour. I shall be glad to furnish you with further particulars if you will not deem it too much trouble</p>
            <p rend="valediction"
               style="font-family: Geneva; font-size: 12pt; margin-left: 1.75in; margin-right: 0in; text-indent: 0in; "
               xml:lang="en">Yours very respectfully</p>
            <p rend="valediction"
               style="font-family: Geneva; font-size: 12pt; margin-left: 1.75in; margin-right: 0in; text-indent: 0in; "
               xml:lang="en">
               <space dim="horizontal" extent="tab"/>Jas H. Smith</p>
            <p rend="valediction"
               style="font-family: Geneva; font-size: 12pt; margin-left: 1.75in; margin-right: 0in; text-indent: 0in; "
               xml:lang="en">
               <space dim="horizontal" extent="tab"/>
               <space dim="horizontal" extent="tab"/>Engraver &amp;c.</p>
            <space dim="vertical" unit="lines" quantity="1"/>
            <space dim="vertical" unit="lines" quantity="1"/>
            <space dim="vertical" unit="lines" quantity="1"/>
         </div>
